  m_text: 'This is Project 1 for Unit GAD315. The goal of the assignemnt was to apply
    Visual Effects in a scene in Unreal. This is done through the Niagara FX system.
    We were given one VFX Archetype and two Expressions to choose from. I chose as
    an Archetype: a Shield. As for the Expressions, I chose Fire and Water.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
