  m_text: This assignment was part of GAD221, Project 2. Our group consisted of me,
    Frank Manford and Lathika Samaraweera. Our theme was a part of 'Meaningful Games'.
    We decided to create an experience that mimics a toxic work environment, via
    implementation of a 'Crunch' mentality that is commongly seen in the entertainment
    industry today. My role was Game Design and and Sound Design.
