  m_text: 'This was a group Project that was done in GAD315 with members: Cameron
    Daly, Nicholas Walsh and Jake Hinrichsen. Our conept was to use Unreal''s Fracture
    System to destroy a Virtual Bridge. My role was Storyboarding, Slight Asset searching
    and editing the final cut of the video In Da Vinci.'
