  m_text: 'This was a group Project I worked on with members: Jayden Holliss, Alex
    Frederick and Lathika. My role was Narrative Director, Writer, Documentation
    and programmer. My role as programmer was never intended but during development
    I felt that since I had plenty of freetime, I helped implement an extra puzzle
    element. I programmed a safe code mechanic. This had an interactable keypad UI
    and I also created a safe model in Blender with an additional animation of the
    safe door opening.'
