  m_text: 'For Uni GAD213, I developed a First Person Horror Puzzle Game. Created
    Within the Unity Engine, the project was inspired by games such as ''Amnesia:
    The Dark Descent'' and various ''Resident Evil'' titles. I used many outsourced
    assets and audio to create the project. The project was a learning experientce
    when learning how to integrate both puzzles and horror.'
